{"tid":998937,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「怡和閃跌八成」怡和業務包圍港人生活","createTime":"2019-01-28T10:45:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-28T11:16:49.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8c74fcd64355d19bce9c755e0ea28c28b28d3dce","tid":998937,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T10:45:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190125/large/b0302a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190125%2Flarge%2Fb0302a.gif&h=8e401321&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【本報訊】老牌英資洋行怡和集團創立近兩個世紀，集團英文名Jardine Matheson為兩個始創家族姓氏，目前由凱瑟克（Keswick）家族掌舵。在殖民地時代，怡和大班長期是香港政府行政局的非官守議員，對香港政治及經濟舉足輕重。<br />\n<br />\n1984年，怡和將公司註冊地點由香港遷往百慕達，並在九十年代將公司及旗下多家子公司由香港轉為新加坡及倫敦上市，影響力大減。不過怡和子公司在港仍經營地產、零售和餐飲等，包圍香港人日常生活。<br />\n<br />\n怡和集團旗下主要有四間公司包括怡和太平洋（Jardine Pacific）、怡和汽車（Jardine Motors）、怡和策略（Jardine Strategic）與怡和保險顧問（Jardine Lloyd Thompson）。<br />\n相關新聞：怡和離奇閃跌八成收市倒升　稱電子交易失誤<br />\n<br />\n包括惠康萬寧<br />\n怡和策略持有牛奶國際78%股權，旗下有連鎖快餐店美心、大型超市惠康、萬寧、便利店7-Eleven、宜家家居、Market Place by Jasons及GNC保健食品等。<br />\n<br />\n怡和集團亦是中環商廈「收租王」，旗下香港置地持有多項物業，包括交易廣場、怡和大廈、置地廣場、歷山大廈、遮打大廈、太子大廈及告羅士打大廈等，合計面積約45.2萬平方米。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20190125/20598903\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190125%2F20598903&d=L9WWkC8qCnSwgTnBr0z%2BTHadZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=c2a235c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190125%2F20598903&h=60fca10d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/daily/article/20190125/20598903</a>  <br />\n<br />\n怡和股價一度暴跌83% 市值縮水410億美元<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/998932\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/998932</a>"},{"pid":"fbce2cee4cb36a2f70553484b09f99a9b1fab1d3","tid":998937,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T10:49:28.000Z","msg":"咩事?"},{"pid":"29329c511dee5cce25a0b3dab3d044a3835d32a0","tid":998937,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T10:50:32.000Z","msg":"投行出錯想取消交易<br />\n點知新加坡交易所唔批准<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82cead9246fac44710513a432922cc51875dda0d","tid":998937,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T11:02:38.000Z","msg":"怡和機器同 怡和電機。。業務上有咩分別？？"},{"pid":"259d4e682828ed4739bbbd6b969235f541735a12","tid":998937,"uid":131423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T11:16:49.000Z","msg":"10蚊買個d就發<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}